   newpath
   10 mm    10 mm   moveto
   200 mm   10 mm   lineto
   200 mm   89 mm   lineto
   10 mm    89 mm   lineto
   closepath
   stroke
grestore

% Boxes for the 5x5 = 25 seed words for Monero
gsave
10 mm 10 mm translate

0 1 4 {
